Bad quality. Same as the others already out.  Scrolling Chinese subs, and ads...on a bootleg. Ads, really? Now there's an angle that can be pursued for prosecution if one really wanted to. All n all though, its not really the uploaders fault.  Its not like they are EVER the ones in the theaters. They are simply the ones willing to post and sometimes pay the bootleggers for their contribution. So, keep in mind. You CAN get paid for camming movies. So go get motivated and not only make a buck for yourself, but in turn, give the rest of us the quality we deserve.
